  <text>
    <body resp="#CM">
      <div type="letter">
        <div corresp="#surface-1">
          <opener>
            <dateline>(Via the Livorno courier)</dateline>
            <lb/><lb/>
            <address>
              To the <orgName ref="#CDC">Electors of the College of Cicagna</orgName>
            </address>
            <lb/><lb/>
            <salute>Brothers!</salute>
          </opener>
          <lb/><lb/>
          <p>
            You, in choosing the man of the people who <sic>debbe</sic>
            must defend and expand your rights; the man
            who represents you in your <choice>
              <sic>da fidari</sic>
              <corr>trusts</corr>
            </choice> and beliefs, 
            <seg>will cast your gaze upon me.</seg> 
            I have nothing but a sword and my conscience; 
            <unclear>ve lo inisaen</unclear>.
          </p>

          <p>
            I have <choice>
              <sic>amaor</sic>
              <corr>loved</corr>
            </choice> you since childhood,
            <choice>
              <sic>udando</sic>
              <corr>listening</corr>
            </choice> 
            <lb/>
            to the history of your fathers; 
            <seg xml:id="c4seg1" ana="#nationalism_rising">in 1846 you responded with
            <lb/>
            your lives</seg> to the proud call of <placeName ref="#GEN">Genoa</placeName>; 
            <seg xml:id="c4seg2" ana="#genoa1800">in 1800</seg> your inspirers <choice>
              <sic>debbene</sic>
              <corr>should</corr>
            </choice> 
            <lb/>
            have led you <choice>
              <sic>male anch√©</sic>
              <corr>poorly as well</corr>
            </choice>
            <lb/>
            into grievous error, yet you proved yourselves
            <lb/>
            men. Now you wish to be men in courage, citi-
            <lb break="no"/>
            zens at heart, and your trust repaid me for
            <lb/>
            long efforts. Thus, that trust strengthens
            <lb/>
            my faith in the souls, so to speak, sworn by a
            <lb/>
            popular vote.
            <lb/>
            I accept it as such. For it, and with it,
            <lb/>
            with guidance and arm, oh brothers, I shall
            <lb/>
            <seg xml:id="c11-seg1" ana="#education">represent you</seg> always.
            <lb/>
          </p>

          <closer>
            <dateline>
              <placeName ref="#GEN">Genoa</placeName>, <date xml:id="dt1" when="1848-10-06">October 6, 1848</date>
            </dateline>
            <lb/><lb/>
            <stamp xml:id="c4-s1"/>
            <signed><persName ref="#GAR">G. Garibaldi</persName></signed>
            <p xml:id="stamp-placeholder"/>
          </closer>
        </div>
